{"tid":1087050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本公布「令和」為新年號","createTime":"2019-04-01T06:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:23:35.000Z","uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"771fa2e32b09e586afa7e7f7ab5521c9e1eaa7d1","tid":1087050,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:19:08.000Z","msg":"日本皇太子德仁下月一日登基，內閣官房長官菅義偉宣布，決定採用「令和」為新年號，取代用了三十年的「平成」年號，並會在德仁登基同日使用。首相安倍晉三稍後召開記者會，解釋新年號的寓意及典故。<br />\n專家懇談會和全體閣僚今早先後舉行會議，敲定新年號。日本舉國關注年號更替，不少民眾到東京皇居聚集，等候公布結果；企業就爭取時間，在下月更換年號前，印好月曆及信紙等用品，以及修改電腦系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/27e1e7/f/800x0/http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190401_20190401-104627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F27e1e7%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190401_20190401-104627.jpg&h=a304193e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/781f37/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190401/20190401_07f9eeb377d2f67cd24dS2LPWy5oeBid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F781f37%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190401%2F20190401_07f9eeb377d2f67cd24dS2LPWy5oeBid.jpg&h=2200e90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咗安久9年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84866e2909aedee25c8b6f05436d8cffce6f1a79","tid":1087050,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"不如開個崇日撚台啦"},{"pid":"7b898642c3f1f5e695717432fcc6e48d94089927","tid":1087050,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"還我安久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />